{
  "stem": "20800.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we live with one day at a time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The longer we can survive, then more chances we be-- we can be free.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were you with anyone in particular in this camp?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In this camp, I start to find out whom I can trust and whom I can't trust, whom I needed, and whom I don't needed, to make sure that the people needed people have a help.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they knew if they seek-- or somebody will found it, so they will put away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- Liuda, that's friend that-- I have letter from her-- from her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her father-- her father was in prison, mother, and she.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was-- she and her mother was in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were sent in the same camp-- working force in--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--this--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--factory.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I have a look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I might find out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She sent me a letter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she-- she-- only Liuda, she told me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I can-- I remember long enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I've forgotten now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- no, no, no, that's Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're not Jewish-- from Buchenwald, no Jewish at all-- all Russian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you see, why I trust Liuda-- because her mother and her father all were the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had a fight in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she helped me a lot to put people sick in hospital that we had on the premises of these factories.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I helped a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because as soon as they were sick and I-- somebody come to me, look, she's sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if she goes, she might-- so straight away, I went to Liuda and said, Liuda, you better ring to doctor, make sure she knows the name who has to-- the number who has to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
